name: real-world-workflow-finder
description: Find real-world agent workflow repos, skill packs, templates, and workflow catalogs similar to a user's idea. Use when the user asks for workflows like an earthquake/building evidence audit, healthcare/referral/patient document workflow, education workflow, real estate workflow, public evidence audit, due diligence workflow, case intake workflow, queue/monitoring/human-review workflow, multi-industry workflow catalog, Codex config package, or similar agentic workflow examples.
